 BEAUTIFUL BEDTIME STORIES BEGIN RIGHT HERE. Ethan Allen bedroom furniture is the perfect foundation for a look that will delight—and last. Built for beauty, strength, and durability, our bed frames, bedroom dressers, and bedside tables are available in an array of sizes, and many can be customized in the finish of your choice. Queen size beds, king beds, and even twin beds can be outfitted with our premier mattresses for the ultimate in comfort. Whether you prefer a firm mattress, a gel mattress, or something slightly softer, you’ll find it in our extensive collection. Luxury bedroom furniture can turn your space into a true oasis—and there's nothing more glamorous than white bedroom furniture. White dressers, night stands, beds, and bedroom tables offer a gorgeous blank canvas for bedding and drapery of any color. 































